OL,3,CHow a 30-year marriage in a peaceful
OL,4,CDevon village ended in violence and
OL,5,Ctragedy
OL,7,FThe village of Knowle in North Devon
OL,8,Fis an idyllic setting. Acres of
OL,9,Frolling green farmland; homes nestled
OL,10,Famong sprawling forests; a picture of
OL,11,Fquiet country village life.
OL,13,FBut on a Sunday afternoon in August
OL,14,F2022, the peace was shattered by .
OL,16,F'He will come and get me'
OL,18,FChristine and Ian Rawle were arguing
OL,19,Fin a stable just behind their isolated
OL,20,Fbungalow.
