OL,7,FAs the row reached its peak, Mrs Rawle
OL,8,Fpicked up a large kitchen knife and
OL,9,Fplunged it 10cm into her husband's
OL,10,Fback. He followed her for a short time
OL,11,Fthrough the fields, before collapsing.
OL,12,FThe emergency services were called but
OL,13,Fthey could not save Mr Rawle, and Mrs
OL,14,FRawle was .
OL,16,FSitting in the back of a police van in
OL,17,Fhandcuffs, she told officers: "How can
OL,18,Fyou love someone who is so nasty to
OL,19,Fyou? He will come and get me and he
OL,20,Fwill kill me."
