OL,12,Fcase ended up in crown court, where a
OL,13,Fjury of seven men and five women heard
OL,14,Fweeks of extraordinary evidence.
OL,16,FThe court was told Mr and Mrs Rawle
OL,17,Fwould play pranks on each other. ,
